AXES
  Substance (Fields) ↔ Structure (Relational Invariants)
  Privileged Observer ↔ Entangled Subsystem
  Global Unitary ↔ Local Records (Decohered Projections)
  Epistemic Credence ↔ Ontic Measure (Born-Weighted Amplitudes)

SATELLITES
  Decoherence: Entanglement with environment yields effective classicality.
  Quantum Darwinism: Objectivity via redundant environmental copying (survivability via copyability).
  Contextuality: Values cannot be assigned independent of measurement context (Kochen-Specker).
  No-go Theorems:
    • Bell → No local hidden variables.
    • PBR → Purely epistemic views require additional structure or collapse.
    • Frauchiger-Renner → Single absolute history + universal unitarity + observer-independent outcomes cannot all hold simultaneously.
  Thermodynamics:
    • Landauer Limit: Erasure allows new measurement; information is physical.

VOID
  ∅ Consciousness as trigger (Thermostats measure too).
  ∅ Naive Realism (Particles as little balls).
  ∅ Local Hidden Variables (Death by Bell).
  ∅ Distinct "Classical World" (It's all quantum, just decohered).
  ⊘ "Infinite Universes" (Branches are effective sectors, not necessarily infinite geography).

TEXTURE
  Geometric. Informational. Relational.
