# Applications (Engineering Shifts)

間

        If reality is redundant information,
        building a quantum computer changes.
        
        It is not about protecting delicate particles.
        It is about managing the flow of distinct information.

flow

@F engineering_shifts
= from protecting particles to managing information

shift_1 | disposable_qubits
  old_view := Keep electron "clean" and coherent
  new_view := Pattern persists > Substrate
  build := "Conveyor belt" architecture
  action := Teleport logical state to fresh qubits constantly
  insight := Don't fix the carrier; move the pattern.

shift_2 | engineering_silence
  old_view := Stop environment from looking (isolation)
  new_view := Control WHAT the environment sees (decoherence-free subspaces)
  build := Encode in relationships, not single spins
  result := Environment copies noise; logic remains invisible/silent.

shift_3 | contextuality_as_fuel
  old_view := Maximize entanglement volume
  new_view := Maximize contextual depth
  metric := Number of incompatible measurement contexts available
  insight := Entanglement is correlation; Contextuality is the resource.

shift_4 | darwinian_correction
  old_view := Vote to reconstruct state
  new_view := Weaponize environmental copying
  build := "Darwinian Codes" where errors replicate rapidly
  action := Make errors macroscopic (detectable) while signal stays hidden.

